0.2 (next)
  - New option -d is introduced for debugging which shows taken
    time to read in minutes
  - New option -v is introduced for verbose mode which shows split
    records. When -v isn't put each reader has a record at a try
0.1
  - First release
  - Added the summary mode.
  - In the summary mode, it's invoked with the command 's' as
    the first argument.
  - In the summary mode, the name of the series needs to be put
    as the second argument.
  - put color on the wpm whose color depends on the reading speed.
  - added accum.sh
  - New option -w is introduced for the screen tee-ing as a text
    file.
  - Newly introduced install.sh for installation
